# CSS Rules

## Design Tokens — Always Use Variables
```css
--bg-deep        /* #0a0a12 — page background */
--bg-card        /* #12121e — card/panel background */
--border-subtle  /* rgba(255,255,255,.08) */
--border-glow    /* rgba(130,80,255,.45) — focus ring */
--text-primary   /* #f0eeff */
--text-muted     /* #a09ab8 */
--text-dim       /* #6b6585 — placeholder, secondary */
--accent         /* #8250ff */
--accent-hover   /* #9b6dff */
```
**Never hardcode hex colors.** Always use `var(--token-name)`.

## Component Checklist (before adding new CSS)
- Does a class already exist in `css/app.css`? Check first.
- New component classes go in `css/app.css` under the matching section comment.
- Page-level `<style>` blocks only for one-off, non-reusable overrides (e.g. hero gradient).

## Input Field Standard
```css
/* Always applied to .input-field — do not override without strong reason */
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
color: var(--text-primary);   /* This prevents white-on-white text */
```

## Spacing & Sizing
- Font sizes: `0.85rem` body, `0.77rem` labels/captions, `0.67rem` descriptions
- Border radius: `0.9rem` cards, `0.65rem` inputs, `0.6rem` buttons
- Shadows: `0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.35)` for cards

## Layout
- Grid and Flexbox only — no floats, no tables for layout.
- `dir-grid` (index.html) uses 6-column CSS grid: `grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr)`
- `dir-item-desc` must stay `white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;` to prevent column misalignment.
